Tata to Build Vehicle Assembly Plant in South Africa, Business Day Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-07-07T05:18:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/tata-to-build-vehicle-assembly-plant-in-south-africa-business-day-says.html
Tata Group  will start building a
vehicle assembly plant in  Pretoria ,  South Africa ’s capital, this
month, Business Day reported, citing Debasis Ray, a company
spokesman.  Ray didn’t give details of how much Tata will invest in the
plant, Business Day reported.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
